synopsis:
A story about a dull protagonist who uses a hypnosis app to hypnotize the woman of his dreams and have sex with her.
There are four main heroines so far.
His classmate, Iori Takanashi;
his gal sister, Haruka Maesawa;
the health committee member, Kaori Hashimoto;
and Iori's mother, Ouka Takanashi.

The story will be told like a branching route in an eroge game.
Depending on the route, they might meet up (3P?) along the way...
